All data contributed to the Causalontology commons - every content object and
every provenance record - is licensed under "The attribution always; no
profit, no problem license.": the same terms as the repository LICENSE file
(the Apache License, Version 2.0 text, as carried by PrologAI and Mentova).

Attribution is always required - and in Causalontology it is also built into
the data itself, because every record carries its signed source.

Owner's decision, 2026-07-13: this single license applies to ALL of it - the
code, the data, the specification, and the architecture. It supersedes the
